msgstr "Vendetta"

#. [side]: type=Horseman Commander, id=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/09a_Vengeance.cfg:47
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/09a_Vengeance.cfg:48
